{
  "texts": [
    "Leveraging external APIs to complement and expand action space is a popular paradigm in recent years.",
    "For example, HuggingGPT [13] leverages the models on HuggingFace to accomplish complex user tasks.",
    "[66,67] propose to automatically generate queries to extract relevant content from external Web pages when responding to user request.",
    "TPTU [67] interfaces with both Python interpreters and LaTeX compilers to execute sophisticated computations such as square roots, factorials and matrix operations.",
    "Another type of APIs is the ones that can be directly invoked by LLMs based on natural language or code inputs."
  ]
}